  "body": "<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f2Ov9dF.png\" width=\"1125\" height=\"450\" /></h5>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/CjkyZq48HU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/323533093015257088?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;label=discord&amp;labelColor=a662b3&amp;color=311836\" width=\"188\" height=\"28\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/pRqUhRqK?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&labelColor=a662b3&color=311836\" width=\"171\" height=\"28\" /></center>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">About🤺:</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Katana's Mod adds <strong>10</strong> new katanas to the game, Katana's have increased speed and similar damage to a sword, some of these katanas require certain mods such as (<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betternether\">Better Nether)</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rkw4s1V.png\" width=\"960\" height=\"160\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Crafting⚔️:</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">To craft a katana you must first craft a blade made with 2 of any tool material (Iron, Stone, Diamond etc.) and combine it with a stick in a crafting table (examples below), Netherite katanas are made through the smithing table like usual.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZF9daLF.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"200\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong> <br /><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/s1ght\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/48730f10-201e-4c9e-afb8-479c0f85aa31.png\" width=\"1134\" height=\"188\" /></a></strong></span></p>\n<p>Optional - Supported Mods:</p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-combat\"><li>Better Combat (HIGHLY RECOMMENDED)</li></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betternether\"><li>Better Nether</li></a>",
